Package gov.nih.nci.ncia.grid

Interface Summary
GridNodeLookup Interface that allows you to look up RemoteSiteDTOs.
RemoteGridNode Interface that provides two methods for grid nodes to implement a caching strategy.
RemoteNodeBuilderStrategy Strategy interface so that a different type of grid node can be built and cached.
